desc_long									更新备注									Update #1Improvements and fixed problems Listed Below :Major :The safe puzzle quit system fixed ,it  didn’t restart the game anymore . Fixed crash problem during first level. People of AI system improved for problems like running into walls Face motion of Amir after talking didn’t go weird any more. Car navigation system improved. No more two slow after starting the car and to fast speed after moving, just one stable speed. Foot step sound synced more precisely with character movementsRun Animation movement of Afshar and amir begin exactly with holding the shift key (no more delay) Fixing collider of afshar in some level that caused him to partially go to the walls Spelling problems fixed and removed and all Persian subtitle fixed. Mouse cursor locked and hided always during gameplay  Y Invert of mouse added Stairs in two levels fixed  Self Defending mini games removed because of it's  damaging to gamplay. Minor :green bar removed from some cutscenesgrafiti on the wall of first cutscene is in English nowmotion blur removed from first level that caused problem Detective clips through the couch a lot during home cutscene.fixed Amir didn't spawn in the air & fall after prison level.Mini map lines now are more precise with Level environmentsThe hotel attendant changed to proper modelMany other minor fixes or polish things in sound effects , collision , etc.																						关于这款游戏							Inspired by true events, Dark Years is set in 1953 Tehran, Iran.Tehran is in the grip of fear following a series of grisly murders. Major Afshar has been tasked with finding those responsible. Meanwhile, some 3,300 miles away in London, an Iranian journalist is handed documents that uncover a conspiracy of seismic proportions. As both the Major and the journalist delve deeper, their paths will cross, plans for a coup will be uncovered and Western government involvement will be exposed.Dark Years is an action-adventure game based on the real events surrounding ‘Operation Ajax ‘. In an attempt to secure the rights to Iran’s oil, the British and American governments secretly backed a coup that over-threw the democratically elected government of Mohammad Mosaddegh. The result was a period of great instability and violence.Key Game FeaturesOpen-world gameplayshooting and drivingOver 25 characters with nearly 3000 lines of dialogueCompelling narrativeOver 8 hours of gameplay						
